- Install bazel:

wget https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazelisk/releases/download/v1.4.0/bazelisk-linux-amd64
sudo chmod +x bazelisk-linux-amd64
sudo mv bazelisk-linux-amd64 /usr/bin/bazel
cd ~/onos
bazel version

+ Clone onos-2.4:
git clone -b onos-2.4 https://github.com/opennetworkinglab/onos.git
